# Plenvo — Personal Finance Flow App

## Project Summary
Bilingual (Arabic RTL / English LTR) personal finance web app. Users track income, expenses, obligations, growth (savings goals, deposits, fixed assets), and investments across **dynamic financial periods** tied to their salary cycle.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 — brand color `#1B6EF3`
- **Backend/Auth**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + RLS + Auth)
- **Charts**: Recharts
- **Icons**: lucide-react

