## Core Concepts

### Financial Period
- Each user sets a `period_start_day` (1–28)
- Period runs from `startDay` of month N to `startDay - 1` of month N+1
- Period key format: `YYYY-MM` (represents the month the period starts)
- Use `getPeriodKey(date, startDay)` and `getPeriodDates(key, startDay)` from `@/lib/period`

### Bilingual Support
- Use `useLanguage()` hook — provides `t(ar, en)`, `locale`, `isRTL`, `toggleLocale`
- `t('عربي', 'English')` — always pass Arabic first, English second
- HTML `dir` and `lang` attributes are set automatically on `<html>` element
- Period date range display is always `dir="ltr"` regardless of app language

### Supabase
- All tables have RLS enabled — always filter by `user_id = auth.uid()`
- Use `createClient()` from `@/lib/supabase/client` in Client Components
- Use `createClient()` from `@/lib/supabase/server` in Server Components/Actions
- Profile is auto-created on signup via trigger; redirect to `/onboarding` if `period_start_day` is null

## UI Conventions
- Brand blue: `#1B6EF3` (use `bg-brand`, `text-brand`, `border-brand`)
- Cards: `bg-white rounded-xl border border-border shadow-sm`
- Inputs: `rounded-xl border border-border focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand`
- Buttons (primary): `bg-brand text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-brand-dark`
- Danger: `text-danger` / `bg-red-50`
- Success: `text-success`
- Warning: `text-warning`
- Surface/background: `bg-surface` (`#F8F9FA`)
